Paradise Weddings is a team of highly educated travel specialist with a heart for making your dream wedding, honeymoon, family or luxury travels a reality. We will give your our full attention to ensure that your dreams become a reality.

A Destination Wedding or Honeymoon is a very special time in a couples lives. My experience and knowledge helps to match dreams with realities, such as budgets. We plan a Wedding to Remember!

Ace Travel House, Inc. is a locally owned travel agency that has been in business in the Houston area for decades. We specialize in Honeymoons and Destination Weddings. Unlike an online travel agency, Ace Travel is a full service, store front travel agency with normal business hours 8:30 am to 5:00 pm, Monday thru Friday and weekends by appointment. Our competent staff works hard to assure our customers the best service possible. We have a close working relationship with all our vendors which allow us to provide a high level of customer satisfaction. Our staff is well traveled so that we are able to give you firsthand knowledge on many top honeymoon and destination wedding properties and locations. We have planned numerous destination weddings all over The Caribbean and Mexico with extremely happy brides. Once you decide on a Destination Wedding, we will take care of getting all your guests travel arrangements booked. We will also help you with planning your wedding details.

Vacations In Paradise is a leading destination wedding specialist travel agency. We provide full service for an all inclusive destination wedding, taking care of your travel needs for the wedding couple and their guests and assisting with communication between the couple and the resort.

I offer professional guidance choosing the top Tour Operators and products! Also helping chose the perfect locations and resorts for the clients’ budget. I have 30 years experience, and love when my clients come back happy! Not only do they come back to me, but they refer friends and family.
